\renewcommand{\cftsubsecfont}{\small\bfseries} % Change font size and style for subsection entries
```

### Step 4: Update the TOC

To update the TOC after making changes to your document, you need to run LaTeX twice. The first run will generate the TOC, and the second run will update the TOC with the correct page numbers.

